title: nacltest.bash: nacl/arm build is borken
body:
The nacl/arm build is currently broken. I suspect this is related to #9732 

```
##### Testing packages.
Error while loading "/tmp/go-build935708356/cmd/addr2line/_test/addr2line.test": Validation failure. File violates Native Client safety rules.
Using the wrong type of nexe (nacl-x86-32 on an x86-64 or vice versa)
or a corrupt nexe file may be responsible for this error.
FAIL	cmd/addr2line	0.308s
```
